  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to LXDE Icon Theme</title>

    <para>
      The <application>LXDE Icon Theme</application> package contains
      nuoveXT 2.2 Icon Theme for <application>LXDE</application>.
    </para>

    &lfs74_checked;

